          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " in a Dodge Charger. That might sound bizarre to most people, but for car enthusiasts it’s not nearly as big of a stretch. Still, there’s more to the story than just a police officer shirking his duties to try out a ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
